#This is for MC B0 -> J/Psi K*0, K*0 -> K- pi+.
#And this is two body decay.
#|H+|,|H-|=0.0, |H0|=1.0
# Decay table to generate
# Upsilon(4S) -> B0 anti-B0 -> Generic
#                |
#                 -> J/Psi K*0
#                    |     |  
#                    |      -> K+ pi-
#                    | 
#                      -> e+e- or mu+mu-.
#
Alias MYB0      B0
Alias MYanti-B0 anti-B0
ChargeConj MYB0 MYanti-B0
Alias MYPSI     J/psi
Alias MYKstar   K*0
Alias MYanti-Kstar anti-K*0
ChargeConj MYKstar MYanti-Kstar
#
# B0-B0bar mixing Delta m in PDG2018
Define dm 0.5064e12
#
Decay Upsilon(4S)
1.000 B0 anti-B0 MYB0 MYanti-B0 VSS_BMIX dm;
Enddecay
#
Decay MYB0
1.000 MYPSI MYKstar SVV_HELAMP 0.6417 3.1633 0.7556 0.0 0.1312 1.5507;
Enddecay
#
Decay MYanti-B0
1.000 MYPSI MYanti-Kstar SVV_HELAMP 0.6417 3.1633 0.7556 0.0 0.1312 1.5507;
Enddecay
#
Decay MYPSI
0.500 e+ e-           PHOTOS VLL;
0.500 mu+ mu-         PHOTOS VLL;
Enddecay
#
Decay MYKstar 
1.000 K+ pi-          PHOTOS VSS;
Enddecay
#
Decay MYanti-Kstar 
1.000 K- pi+          PHOTOS VSS;
Enddecay
#
End
